Haunted House 3D Screensaver

Link: http://www.screensavers-store.com/

Get the Halloween mood with the Haunted House 3D Screensaver! Screensaver 
provides users with a spooky way to let their computer rest. By taking you
on a tour of an old Gothic-style haunted house on a dark and misty night in
4K, this fun tool will certainly give your computer some personality. A full
Moon shines brightly overhead as the camera hovers over the yard, where a 
mysterious man walks around with a lantern. Inside the house, lights turn on 
randomly behind the windows.

Developer: 3Planesoft
